name: Run a self-driving car using JavaScript and TensorFlow.js
shortDescription: Demonstration of how to train a self-driving car to steer and to drive autonomously in Udacity Self-Driving Car Simulator using TensorFlow.js.
longDescription: Demonstration of how to train a self-driving car to steer and to drive autonomously in Udacity Self-Driving Car Simulator using TensorFlow.js.
